
                       Information about application
                       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. General information
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   This is an sizing application for calculate EI core choking coils.
   This is a software, which does not cost money (maybe you must pay for
use Internet). The lope conditions is the acceptance and observance of
the General Public Licence.
   
   OS support: Linux and Windows.
   Language support: English and Hungarian.

2. Installer packages
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. for Linux
   chc-0.1-i586.tar.gz         binary package
   chc-0.1-i586.bin            installer programme
   chc_0.1-1_i386.deb          binary package

b. for Windows
   chc-0.1-win32.zip           binary package
   chc-0.1-win32.exe           installer application

c. source code
   chc-0.1.tar.gz              source package

3. Settings
~~~~~~~~~~~
   On linux use 'LANG' environment variable to set language of the
   application.

   for example: English:   en_US,
                Hungarian: hu_HU

